OL,3,CBaby loss charity delivers 'cooling
OL,4,Ccot' to hospital to support grieving
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FThe parents of a stillborn baby girl
OL,8,Fare trying to offer comfort to
OL,9,Ffamilies going through something
OL,10,Fsimilar.
OL,12,FJo and David Ward delivered a special
OL,13,Frefrigerated bereavement cot to Medway
OL,14,FMaritime Hospital - the same place
OL,15,Fwhere the couple gave birth to their
OL,16,Fdaughter Abigail, who was stillborn at
OL,17,F41 weeks.
