OL,4,Ccot' to hospital to support grieving
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FThe 'Abi Cooling Cot' allows a
OL,8,Fgrieving family to spend more time
OL,9,Fwith their child because it can keep
OL,10,Fthem at a lower temperature.
OL,12,FThe couple, who founded baby loss
OL,13,Fcharity Abigail's Footsteps, named the
OL,14,Fcot after their daughter and called
OL,15,Fthem her "lasting legacy."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
