OL,7,FSupporting the charity is former Bucks
OL,8,FFizz singer and TV presenter Cheryl
OL,9,FBaker, who is also a Vice President of
OL,10,FAbigail's Footsteps.
OL,12,FJoining the couple at the hospital to
OL,13,Fhand over the cot, she shared that she
OL,14,Fonce almost lost her own baby.
OL,16,FShe said: "To give birth to a baby
OL,17,Fthat you've been carrying for nine
OL,18,Fmonths and for it not to be breathing,
OL,19,FI can't explain - I could never
OL,20,Fexplain - how much it hurts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
