OL,7,F"The doctors and nurses, they saved
OL,8,Fher. I was one of the lucky ones
OL,10,F"If parents sadly have a stillborn
OL,11,Fbaby and they want to raise money to
OL,12,Fbuy an Abi cot, there's a plaque
OL,13,Fthat's put on the front that says "in
OL,14,Fmemory of", and there's a little heart
OL,15,Fthat you can take away and so they can
OL,16,Fhave that as a memory."
