OL,4,Ccot' to hospital to support grieving
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,FThe cooling cot has been delivered to
OL,8,Fa bereavement suite at Medway Maritime
OL,9,FHospital, called 'Abigail's Place'.
OL,10,FIt's designed to be a place of safety
OL,11,Fand solace for parents.
OL,13,FBereavement Support Midwife, Dannii
OL,14,FBurnett, said the reaction to the
OL,15,Fsuite is "always beautiful."
OL,17,F"It comprises of a kitchen, living
OL,18,Froom, bedroom and bathroom.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
