OL,3,CBaby loss charity delivers 'cooling
OL,4,Ccot' to hospital to support grieving
OL,5,Cparents
OL,7,F"It's soundproofed. It's away from the
OL,8,Fclinical area and hearing lots of
OL,9,Fnoises of women giving birth and
OL,10,Fbabies crying.
OL,12,F"People are always blown away by how
OL,13,Fpeaceful it is, how little it feels
OL,14,Flike a hospital."
OL,16,FAbigail's Footsteps has delivered
OL,17,Fnearly 300 cots across the country
OL,18,Fover the years, hoping to offer some
OL,19,Fcomfort in a parent's darkest hour.
